I am extremely satisfied with the consultation. Dr. S Balamurugan was very approachable. He spent maximum time to discuss the issue and diagnosed accurately. I said normal. then he prescribed medicines and asked whether to come for review. he said not necessary and he wrote his no.in prescription and told to call me to his no.and I left from his room and bought medicines in the appollo pharmacy. dr.balamurugan and the staff was very good,  friendly and kind.

Recommended.
